1. Definition (interview ready)

Structural Design Patterns wo patterns hote hain jo classes aur objects ko is tarah
organize karte hain ki system flexible, efficient aur easy-to-maintain rah

2. Core Idea (samajh le seedha)

Creational = creation control
Structural = composition control
kaun kis se baat karega
👉 kaise wrap hoga
👉 kaise extend hoga bina tod-fod ke

3. Main Structural Patterns (7 types)

1. Adapter 🔌
2. Bridge
3. Composite 🌳
4. Decorator 🎁
5. Facade 🏢
6. Flyweight 🪶
7. Proxy 🛡️


Features
Structure improve karta hai
Code reusable hota hai
Complexity hide karta hai
System flexible banata hai

Advantages
✔ Loose coupling
✔ Code readability improve
✔ Reusability high
✔ System scalable

Disadvantages (ground reality)
❌ Extra abstraction = confusion
❌ Debugging tough ho sakta hai
❌ Over-design ka risk


